Asia-Pacific
Asia-Pacific is expected to witness the highest growth due to expanding industrial activities and demand from emerging economies like China and India.
The growing pharmaceutical and electronics sectors are key drivers of 4,4′-Dipyridyl consumption in the region.
Rest of the World
Other regions, including Latin America and the Middle East, are seeing steady demand due to increased industrialization and development in the chemical and pharmaceutical sectors.
